<h1 class="ttl-h1">
<span class="ttl-h1__text">高齢でも病気でも、殺処分から救われた犬たちの命をつなぎたい</span>
</h1>
<p class="gcf-lyt-detail__section--head__category">カテゴリー：<a href="/gcf/project/category/1026">動物&nbsp;</a></p>
<div class="gcf-lyt-image2">
<div class="gcf-lyt-image2__image">
<img src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/forms/20210512/d_e53fbf44134c4de0bf4969657e548ddd6a75a1cf.jpg" alt="main_img" decoding="async" />
<ul class="gcf-lst-sns mT24" id="socialbuttons">
